{
  "stem": "2578.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But right after, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the Germans gave out all sorts of orders, especially for the Jews, that they were curfewed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From 7 o'clock-- from 5 o'clock in the afternoon until 7 o'clock in the morning, they were not allowed to go in the-- to be in the streets.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So naturally, this was-- in those days it looked to us that it was a big inconvenience for us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not realizing, of course, what was awaiting us later on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But soon we started to learn when the orders came, for instance, that we are not to leave the houses after 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in order to enforce these kind of laws, they would kill Jews in the streets, not only because they didn't obey the order, only just to show that they mean business.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And to make sure that this will influence the others in case they intend to do something which would look to the Germans that they are breaking or they are not obeying the laws that they are telling us to obey.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, exactly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To set an example for others.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Soon after that, one order came after the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And each order was accompanied by a sentence that ended 'whoever will disobey will be shot.' And they started to ask, especially the Jews, to give up valuable things.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They started out with pots and pans, with copper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then they continued with silverware, any kind of silver pieces.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they ended with jewelry, watches, and diamonds, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They enforced it by going into the houses and search the houses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they will drag out people if they found anything in the house.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
